id=moon-ssh
name=Moon SSH Autostart
version=v0.3.1
versionCode=4
author=jay
description=Enters the Ubuntu 26.04 chroot at /data/data/com.termux/files/home/ubuntu and starts sshd on port 2222 at boot. Invokes ssh_setup.sh. Log at /var/log/moon-ssh-boot.log (in-chroot path; preamble at /data/local/tmp/moon-ssh-boot.log until the chroot path is reachable).
